"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/514758","Department for Education","false","2016-04-28","<p>My Rt Hon Friend the Secretary of State for Education frequently meets Hon Members from across the political spectrum in the performance of her duties.</p><p> </p><p>Information in the form requested is not readily available and could be compiled only at disproportionate cost.</p>","Bognor Regis and Littlehampton","Nick Gibb",,"2016-04-28T15:28:46.59Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/514758/answer","Biography information for Nick Gibb","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/514758/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/514758/answer","Bognor Regis and Littlehampton","Nick Gibb","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/514758/answer/previousversion/57660","Biography information for Nick Gibb","60","Education","Education","2016-04-21","Department for Education: Members","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Education, how many requests to meet with hon. Members she has received from each of the political parties represented in the House since her appointment.","false","Biography information for Kevin Brennan","Cardiff West","Kevin Brennan","35059"
